name: AutoGansta
description:
BYOG Exclusive - Made within 48 hours. AutoGansta :P.

You are to drive an Autorickshaw, also known as the Indian Taxi, collect packages within the city throughout the given time. 

Themes used - 

Unlearn - you are thought to drive an Autorickshaw in roads but at the end you go up however the way you want to just recieve the package. 

One second - Each package you collect adds a second to your total time. 

Jump gone wrong - The roads are a bit higher, so once you jump of the road, your jump might go wrong and you'd lose. Take care.
